<p class="ayah 79-13" id="13" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فَإِنَّمَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Then only</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">هِىَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">it</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">زَجْرَةٌ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(will be) a shout</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَٲحِدَةٌ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">single,</span></span></span> <span class="verse-number"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>13<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></span></p>
<p class="ayah 79-14" id="14" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فَإِذَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">And behold!</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">هُم</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">They</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">بِٱلسَّاهِرَةِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(will be) awakened.</span></span></span> <span class="verse-number"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>14<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></span></p>
