<p class="ayah 79-35" id="35" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يَوْمَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(The) Day</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يَتَذَكَّرُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">will remember</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلْإِنسَـٰنُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">man</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">what</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">سَعَىٰ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">he strove (for),</span></span></span> <span class="verse-number"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>35<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></span></p>
